2.   Register for the institutional repository program here and submit your API key: [https://www.elsevier.com/solutions/sciencedirect/forms/institutional-repository-managers?rURL=Direct](https://www.elsevier.com/solutions/sciencedirect/forms/institutional-repository-managers?rURL=Direct). The Elsevier integration support team will add the ScienceDirect IR settings to your API key, and confirm back. If your institution already has a Scopus API key, you can submit this API key to have the settings for the SD IR services added.

